      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING KIMELI (5) spotted a start but wound up strongly to place when 2.5 lengths third (19.78) at Capalaba in Grade 5. Won at his only start from this box. Must come into calculations. SMOKY CHIPOTLE (1) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at nine of 19 starts including four wins but missed the frame latest when fourth (20.07) over 366m at Capalaba. Will go close here with a clear run. CANYA FLAVOUR (4) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 520m behind Canya Dynamite (30.47) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. One of the better hopes. OLIVER HALF (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
